1. Pokušavala sam da te nazovem sinoć, ali nisam mogla da te dobijem. (*Pokušavala* - Past tense, feminine singular) (I tried to call you last night, but I couldn't reach you.)
2. *Pokušavala* bih da razumem tvoje mišljenje, ali je teško. (Conditional, feminine singular) (I would try to understand your opinion, but it's difficult.)
3. Ona je *pokušavala* da sakrije svoju tugu od drugih. (Past tense, feminine singular) (She tried to hide her sadness from others.)
4. Kada budem imao više vremena, *pokušavat* ću da učim strani jezik. (Future tense, masculine singular) (When I have more time, I will try to learn a foreign language.)
5. Da li si ikada *pokušavao* da otvoriš ovu flašu? (Past tense, masculine singular) (Have you ever tried to open this bottle?)
6. *Pokušavajući* da pronađe rešenje, došao je do neočekivanog otkrića. (Present participle) (Trying to find a solution, he made an unexpected discovery.)
7. Nikada neću *pokušati* da promenim tvoj način razmišljanja. (Future tense, masculine singular) (I will never try to change your way of thinking.)
8. Uvek *pokušavaj* da budeš ljubazan prema drugima. (Imperative, masculine singular) (Always try to be kind to others.)
9. Kada su *pokušavali* da izbegnu gužvu, izgubili su se u šumi. (Past tense, plural) (When they tried to avoid the crowd, they got lost in the woods.)
10. Ona će *pokušavati* da popravi svoje greške i postane bolja osoba. (Future tense, feminine singular) (She will try to fix her mistakes and become a better person.)